      "title": "Sri Lanka won the first medal",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thilanga Isura Kumara of Sri Lanka has won bronze in the 55 kg weightlifting event at the 2022 Commonwealth Games in Birmingham, England.",
        "It is noteworthy that this is Sri Lanka's first medal and he has won a bronze medal in the 225 kg weightlifting event."
      ],
